title: Fly Fishing Still Waters - (Chironomid Techniques)
description:
Fly Fishing Still Waters - (Chironomid Techniques)

DESCRIPTION:
This Video is the first in the "Fly Fishing Still Waters" Series of Videos produced by "Sport Fishing On The Fly". Your hosts for the Video are Brian Chan and Don Freschi. Brian is a senior fisheries biologist in British Columbia, Canada and has been fly fishing for over 30 years. Don is the producer/co-host of the popular TV Show "Sport Fishing On The Fly", which has been in syndication since 1995 with over 120 episodes aired. Don has also been fly fishing for over 25 years.

Join Brian and Don as they show you everything you need to know to be a successful and competent Chironomid fisherman. You will learn the life cycle of the Chironomid, how to fish different line setups and how to tie four special Chironomid patterns. This 75 minute Video is a must have for all fly fishermen looking to improve their skills on Still Waters.

Enjoy & Please Seed!
